high_descs: Turn around and go to the counter above the dishwasher.
Open the top cupboard and remove the brown bowl on the left side of the bottom shelf.
Turn to your right and go to the refrigerator to your immediate right.
Place the bowl in the refrigerator, on the right shelf, above the potato, wait a moment for the bowl to chill, then remove the bowl from the refrigerator.
Turn to your left and go to the sink.
Place the bowl in the bottom, left cupboard, under the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled bowl in the cupboard.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the fridge then turn left and walk to the counter and look up.
Look in the cupboard by your head and pick up the bowl that's in there before closing the cupboard doors.
Turn around and walk to the fridge and when you get there turn left to face it.
Chill the bowl in the fridge then get it back out and close the door.
Turn around and take a step then turn right.
Open the left cupboard door under the sink and put the bowl down there before closing the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold bowl in the cupboard.

high_descs: Move to the counter top to the right side of the sink
Pick up the bowl on the counter top to the right of the sink
Carry the bowl to the left over to the black fridge
Place the bowl in the fridge then shut the door then remove the bowl
Carry the bowl to the white cupboard on the left under the sink
Place the bowl in the cupboard then shut the door
anns.task_desc: Move a brown bowl to the cupboard under the sink
